
<div id='about_div'>
	<h2>Status of Site</h2>
	<p>Currently only of a few monitors listed, and plan on adding more and possibly other products besides monitors.If you have a comments or requests about this humble site please email me using the form below.Thanks for visting!
</div>
<div id='email_div'>
	<%= form_for @contact do |f| %>
		<%=f.label :name %><br>
		<%=f.text_field :name %>
		<%=f.label :email,'Your Email' %><br>
		<%=f.text_field :email %>
		<%=f.label :message %><br>
		<%=f.text_area :message, as: :text %>	
		<div class='hidden'>
			<%=f.label :nickname %><br>
			<%=f.text_field :nickname, hint: 'leave blank please' %>			
		</div>	
		<%= f.submit 'Send Email'%>
	<%end%>

</div>